<algdata>

  <algorithm_statement>Applying clay plaster to walls in one person hour</algorithm_statement>
  <algorithm_math>0,8 m2 dressed in 1 p-h</algorithm_math>
  <variables>
    <var1>
      <unit>p-h</unit><description></description>
      <op>var2 / 0,8</op>
    </var1>
    <var2>
      <unit>m2</unit><description></description>
      <op>var1 * 0,8</op>
    </var2>
  </variables>

</algdata>



<algnotes>

  <general_notes>According to the author, clay plaster of  5 cm thickness was applied to walls including mixing and smoothing it.</general_notes>
  <biblio_notes>The application was done to stone walls using a trowel.</biblio_notes>

</algnotes>



